<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Nikolaus Heinlein, Dekan von St. Jakob zu Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um Verweisung der Klage gegen Veif N., Jude zu Nürnberg, vom geistlichen Gericht [zu Bamberg] an das Reichsgericht zu Nürnberg, da die Judenschaft der Stadt dazu privilegiert ist, und verweist auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_512" id="255r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_512_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Nyclaſen <expan>Dechand<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l17">Jacob cʒu Bamberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_512_r1l18">Erſamer vnd lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erſamkeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l19">voꝛmals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von </del> den veyfs <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l20">bey vns geſeſſen als der v̈mb etlich cʒuſprüch nemlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l21">von geſuchs wegen für euch auf geiſtlıch gerihte <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l22">woꝛden iſt . herheym für des heıligen Reẏchs gerihte cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l23">vveiſen . Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> aber . daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Juden noch alſo herheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l24">weiſen wöllet / Als des <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dy Judiſcheit 
<del rend="strikethrough">hie </del> bey vns geſeſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l25">von <expan>Romiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> keyſern vnd künigen / Vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> auch </del> darcʒu von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> heiligen vater ~ dem Babſte in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Concilio cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l27">Coſtencʒ . gefreyet vnd auch <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>Allergnedig<ex>ſten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_line_1592200496358_1398"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künig gefreyet worden iſt / Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l31">Vnd het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dhein <expan>klag<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_512_r1l30">vmb ſolch ſach </ab></add> iht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_512_r1l32"><expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc vt ın <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_512" id="255r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Nyclasen,
                                                  <expan>dechand<ex>en</ex></expan> czu sant Jacob
                                                czu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als
                                                wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ersamkeit vormals
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den Veyfs
                                                  <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns gesessen,
                                                als der ümb etlich czusprüch nemlich von gesuchs
                                                wegen für euch auf geistlich gerihte
                                                  <expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> worden ist,
                                                herheym für des heiligen reychs gerihte czu weisen,
                                                also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> aber, daz ir
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> juden noch also
                                                herheim weisen wöllet, als des
                                                  <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dy judischeit bey uns
                                                gesessen von <expan>romisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                keysern und künigen und darczu von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> heiligen vater dem
                                                babste in <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> concilio czu
                                                Costencz gefreyet und auch
                                                  <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>allergnedig<ex>sten</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> künig gefreyet
                                                worden ist. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> dhein
                                                  <expan>klag<ex>er</ex></expan> czu
                                                  <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>umb solch sach</add> iht
                                                  <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                                  <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                                                  <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
